item.description: 2020 年 6 月 2 日（星期二） 今日待办 编程 shell keyword vs reserved word vs builtin reserved word 保留字 Keyword, reserved word, and builtin are all the “first word” of a Simple command. Could be placed in two groups: Keyword and Builtin. The two are mutually exclusive. A word (token) can be either a Keyword or a builtin, but not both. 为什么 time 是 keyword，而不是 builtin To allow the existence of a command as the second word.
